:<font size="15">צמח</font></div>

===Pronunciation===
צמח / tsâmach / tsaw-makh'

===Etymology===
A primitive root; 

===Verb===
'''צמח'''

# to sprout (transitively or intransitively, literally or figuratively): - bear, bring forth, (cause to, make to) bud (forth), (cause to, make to) grow (again, up), (cause to) spring (forth, up).

